{"type":null,"faqId":21077,"title":"4G手机用不了4G网络，只有3G网络怎么回事？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1）目前国内4G网络还在建设中，很多地区没有4G信号或者4G信号很差，手机不驻留4G网络很正常；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2）确保你用对了卡：各运营商支持的4G频段都不一样，联通手机不能使用移动的4G网络，移动不能使用联通的4G网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3) 检查Settings中的设置：设置-&gt;移动网络-&gt;网络模式，看看是否选择了3G/2G模式；</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":7,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4740","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1426837645000,"seriesProductName":"Pine-CL00,Pine-CL10,Pine-TL00M,Pine-TL10,Pine-TL20,Pine-UL00","visitedTimes":370,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}